    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">PIN Time Limit Notice</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Announcement of intentions of planned procurements in view of shortening time limits for reception of tenders. Additional information: Where contracting authorities have published a prior information notice which was not itself used as a means of calling for competition, the minimum time limit for the receipt of tenders may be shortened.</skos:definition>
    <skos:historyNote xml:lang="en">WG approval 09/10/2025</skos:historyNote>
  </rdf:Description>
