    <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">The eProcurement Ontology Evaluation core describes the concepts and properties representing the European Public Procurement Evaluation domain. The provision of these semantics offers the basis for a common understanding of the domain for all stakeholders ensuring the quality of data exchange and transparency. The ontology restrictions are published in a separate artefact.</dcterms:description>
